		                Magento 2 debugging tools 

1) Download & install 
	 https://github.com/vpietri/magento2-developer-quickdevbar

2) To enable magento 2 profiler + add SQL queries profiler
	https://github.com/mirasvit/module-profiler

3) Follow the installation procedure/commands listed in above github.



            	Alternate way of enabling Magento2 profler

	> By adding the below code to the root folder index.php
          $_SERVER['MAGE_PROFILER']=1;
		
			or
        > By adding SetEnv MAGE_PROFILER “html” to .htaccess.





